videos.headline: Jeremy Larkin runs the ball in 1-yd for Northwestern TD
John Moten IV runs in for TD for Northwestern
videos.description: Northwestern's John Moten IV runs the ball from the 2-yard line for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Elijah Sindelar pass complete to Rondale Moore for TD
videos.description: Purdue's Elijah Sindelar throws a complete pass to Rondale Moore, who runs for 32 yards for Purdue's first points of the game.

videos.headline: Purdue CB carted off after collision with teammate
videos.description: Purdue CB Simeon Smiley collides with teammate Tim Cason trying to defend a pass. Smiley would be tended to before being carted off.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdue CB carted off after collision with teammate) 2018/08/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Northwestern punches it in before halftime
videos.description: Northwestern RB Jeremy Larkin keeps it himself on option play to extend Wildcats lead to 14.

videos.headline: Purdue late personal foul seals game for Northwestern
videos.description: Northwestern RB Jeremy Larkin  gets stuffed at the line, but gets bailed out by a Purdue unnecessary roughness penalty.
